 -United Democratic Front (UDF) led by businessman Bakili Muluzi
 -Alliance For Democracy (AFORD) led by trade unionist Chakufwa Chihana
 -Malawi Democratic Party (MDP) led by political scientist Kamlepo Kalua
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
