FT  16 MAY 94 / Observer: Up in court
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Observer has to confess, without a trace of sycophancy of course, that it is
becoming impressed by the global reach of Pearson, the FT's parent - and we
are not talking about circling the world in the company of the BBC.
The nomination by Bill Clinton of Judge Stephen Breyer from Massachusetts to
